These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, hedgehog
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, iris
1. the owner of the goat is the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Pet   | goat | hedgehog | lizard    |
| Flower     | marigold    | iris       | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, traveling
3 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, whist
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby     | traveling | woodworking | cooking  |
| Game   | billiard  | mah-jongg  | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, car
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, whist
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Transport           | car | helicopter | skateboard |
| Game   | domino        | whist    | snooker        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, towering, pakistani
House: tower, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the pakistani is on the left of the towering##1
2. the pakistani is on the left or right of the towering##3
3. the tower house is between the pakistani and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | towering | brazilian |
| House     | cape-cod  | tower    | ranch-style  |

