.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, azalea, sunflower
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, chef, journalist
1. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
2. the chef is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsazalea and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Flower   | azalea | orchid | sunflower |
| Job     | chef   | entrepreneur   | journalist   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, chestnut, red
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Color   | red | yellow | chestnut      |
| Pet     | rabbit  | cat | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, fanta
City: hannover, edinburgh, rome
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage   | juice  | fanta    | tea       |
| City   | edinburgh | rome | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, prince, bolivar
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, balloon-flower
1. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | bolivar        | prince  | baccarat   |
| Flower       | balloon-flower | lily | orchid |

