.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, soccer
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, juice
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Sport           | lacrosse | basketball | soccer |
| Beverage   | juice    | sprite | tea     |

