.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine, lilac
3 different pets are kept: horse, bird, guinea-pig
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Color   | lilac | aquamarine         | ebony          |
| Pet        | horse | bird | guinea-pig |

