.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, ship, taxi
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, june
1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the ship##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Transport      | ship    | taxi    | scooter  |
| Birthday   | december | april | june |

