2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to hamburg##2
4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon | domino |
| City           | nizza    | marseilles    | hamburg       |

