.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, kiwi, pineapple
House: wooden, art-deco, farmhouse
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the farmhouse house is the farmhouse house##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Food   | pineapple    | orange   | kiwi |
| House   | art-deco | farmhouse | wooden |

