.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, june
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, handball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Birthday       | june    | january | july  |
| Sport   | handball | basketball        | rowing |

