.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
3 different games are played: snooker, chess, backgammon
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, boat
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Game      | backgammon    | chess | snooker         |
| Transport   | boat | scooter  | roller |

 